{"tid":1279594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「極危險」何老妖又散播仇恨言論","createTime":"2019-07-02T17:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:38:18.000Z","uid":95838,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f98defebe0eaabf02877a534e30c93a1eae242cc","tid":1279594,"uid":95838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QznBcMm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQznBcMm.png&h=03287dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好屌住，其他人係facebook分享我先睇到條片，我簡單總結下條片講咩：<br />\n1. 詆毁宗教 <br />\n2. 侮辱法官<br />\n3. 與媒體為敵<br />\n4. 侮辱八大學生會<br />\n5. 質疑教育政策<br />\n6. 拎6月30號遊行打J<br />\n7. 重複7.1係手足係暴徒<br />\n仲有好多等等 唔建議大家比view數佢 免得佢打J<br />\n<br />\n重點係依條片會令到中間，淺藍，中產，政治冷感既人有所動搖，我嘗試以我家母mindset（深藍）去代入件事，係一定一定會影響到！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家report: 散播仇恨言論（包括條直播同個page)<br />\n我有睇到直播個comment一面倒都係深藍陣營，撐犬等等"},{"pid":"1d9142274e3718d3682d2b391fcb000e0d084b2e","tid":1279594,"uid":95838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"咁都收負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48df48ab521265bd21c6753b28a9cc6ce20add60","tid":1279594,"uid":95838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!!!"},{"pid":"29ec0937ab3c9306207b94901e5331c3da3a37f4","tid":1279594,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:11:49.000Z","msg":"唔禁開 聽唔到聲就唔計 view數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba85067cc25f946296940b7aef67a9fb35e5874","tid":1279594,"uid":95838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!!"},{"pid":"08142401025af42791ca1f388f59f2de5f4e5fd8","tid":1279594,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}